{"tid":1512721,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【因航】吳敏兒指至今已有20名空勤人員被無理解僱","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:02:00.000Z","uid":66271,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"082ba798a869076314612a036443fa9a3582ab04","tid":1512721,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:05:42.000Z","msg":"職工盟主席吳敏兒表示, 至今已知道有20名空勤人員, 被無理解僱, 國泰和港龍航空是重災區.<br />\n        吳敏兒在一個電台節目中指, 有被解僱的人獲公司告知, 因為讚好社交網站上的言論, 或購買外地有頭版支持本港反修例示威廣告的報章, 放到社交網站, 而被公司解僱, 亦有人並無社交網站帳戶, 但被告知在禁飛中國境內名單上, 顯示並無生產力, 所以要解僱.<br />\n        職工盟發起集會, 要求國泰航空在反修例事件上, 不應「跪低」, 但在國泰城的集會被警方反對, 上訴亦被駁回, 因此, 改為申請下午4時至晚上7時, 在中區愛丁堡廣場舉行, 已獲警方批出不反對通知書."},{"pid":"70e3843e177c7fc03843904bd94a723374ae331a","tid":1512721,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8221d7a266f70a85313e3c408e746c944e437c0","tid":1512721,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=6b20cb9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=02209e31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=f52073f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupr